# Warm up

## Announcements

-   Project presentations are Monday! Come see me during office hours or schedule an office hour with me.

## Setup {.smaller}


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# load packages
library(countdown)
library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)
library(mgcv)
library(colorspace)
library(broom)
library(emmeans)
library(ungeviz)
library(ggridges)
library(tidybayes)
library(pkgsimon)
library(dviz.supp)
library(ggpubr)
library(ggtext)
library(extrafont)
library(ggstance)
library(gganimate)
library(emo)

# set theme for ggplot2
ggplot2::theme_set(ggplot2::theme_minimal(base_size = 14, base_family = "Myriad Pro"))

# set width of code output
options(width = 65)

# set figure parameters for knitr
knitr::opts_chunk$set(
  fig.width = 7, # 7" width
  fig.asp = 0.618, # the golden ratio
  fig.retina = 3, # dpi multiplier for displaying HTML output on retina
  fig.align = "center", # center align figures
  dpi = 300 # higher dpi, sharper image
)

loadfonts(device = "all")
```
:::


